'''基雅·梅尔弗顿'''（{{lang-en|Kiah Melverton}}，{{bd|1996年|11月5日||}}）生于昆士兰州南港，是一名澳大利亚女子游泳[[运动员|运动员]]，主攻中长距离自由泳，所属俱乐部是TSS Aquatics<ref>{{cite web |title=Eleven Rookies Join Rio Stars |url=https://www.swimming.org.au/NewsCentral/Twelve-rookies-join-Rio-stars-for-World-Short-Cour.aspx |work=Swimming Australia |accessdate=2018-09-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180901222731/https://www.swimming.org.au/NewsCentral/Twelve-rookies-join-Rio-stars-for-World-Short-Cour.aspx |archive-date=2018-09-01|language=en}}</ref>。她一开始从事的是冲浪救生运动，之后顺带开始从事游泳运动<ref name="GoldCoast">{{cite web |title=Kiah Melverton |url=https://results.gc2018.com/en/swimming/athlete-profile-n6029903-kiah-melverton.htm |work=Gold Coast 2018 |accessdate=2019-07-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190725133553/https://results.gc2018.com/en/swimming/athlete-profile-n6029903-kiah-melverton.htm |archive-date=2019-07-25|language=en}}</ref>。梅尔弗顿除了参加泳池比赛外，也有参加[[公开水域游泳|公开水域游泳]]，她曾获得2017年世界游泳锦标赛公开水域项目的参赛资格<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.swimming.org.au/NewsCentral/McLoughlin-and-Melverton-make-successful-switch-wi.aspx |title=McLoughlin and Melverton make successful switch with selection for World Championships |work=Swimming Australia|accessdate=2018-09-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180902085637/https://www.swimming.org.au/NewsCentral/McLoughlin-and-Melverton-make-successful-switch-wi.aspx |archive-date=2018-09-02|language=en}}</ref>。

